name: Kasha
desc: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned (from your hand) by controlling 2 or more Zombie monsters, and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card is Special Summoned: Shuffle as many other monsters on the field as possible into the Deck, and if you do, this card's ATK becomes 1000 x the number of face-up monsters shuffled into the Deck this way, whose original type was Zombie.
